Description: distro-agnostic Tor transparent proxy manager
 AnonSurf helps route workstation traffic through a private Tor instance.
 .
 This Rust rewrite provides a privileged D-Bus daemon, clap CLI,
 GTK4/libadwaita GUI, private Tor configuration, dedicated firewall rules,
 DNS rollback snapshots, and conservative repair tooling.
